<paragraph blockId="8.[189,1037,1266,1293]" box="[189,1037,1266,1293]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">
MEASUREMENTS. Length: 9.0 mm, elytral length: 
<quantity box="[753,846,1266,1293]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.8" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" unit="mm" value="6.8">6.8 mm</quantity>
, width: 
